<doc id="1274351" wikidata="Q6041272" url="?curid=1274351" title="Instituto Abel">
<text>Instituto Abel is a 1st through 12th grade school in Niterói, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil established in 1950. The Institute follows the philosophy of Jean-Baptiste de la Salle, the French patron saint of Christian teachers.

